              <div class="field__item">
  <div class="full pad_both contained paragraph paragraph--type--row-basic paragraph--view-mode--default" id="section-1043">
            
<div class="content-wrapper">
    
            <div class="field field--name-field-column field--type-entity-reference-revisions field--label-hidden field--count-1 field__item">
  <div class="paragraph paragraph--type--col-text paragraph--view-mode--default" id="section-1042">
            
<div class="text-wrapper">
    
            <div class="clearfix text-formatted field field--name-field-long-text field--type-text-long field--label-hidden field--count-1 field__item"><div class="column-left">At Pepper, we're fortunate to partner with leading organizations on projects and causes that initiate&nbsp;progress. Whether breathing new life into&nbsp;a crumbling structure, adding to the city skyline or preparing a space&nbsp;for healing, the visions&nbsp;that inspire&nbsp;the spaces we build give meaning to our work.&nbsp;</div>

<div class="column-right">Our experts understand the unique considerations of your facility, and we will work with you to develop a plan that's right for you. To learn more about our expertise, search the&nbsp;projects below&nbsp;by market and&nbsp;by story. If you don't&nbsp;find what you're looking for, let us know <a href="#" title="contact us">how we can help</a>.</div>
</div>
      
  </div>
          </div>
</div>
      
  </div>
          </div>
</div>
          </div>
  
  </article>

